{"tid":767843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美媒指廣電總局無解釋原因 中共封殺維尼　新片禁映","createTime":"2018-08-05T01:49:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T07:00:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"6e1e56cf0a81bd665957a08a85f2492eba12fb36","tid":767843,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:49:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180805/20469017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180805%2F20469017&d=%2FyshlLpn4ccxj6cNBwbS8ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=94479556\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180805%2F20469017&h=2e129dbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180805/20469017</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月05日 <br />\n<br />\n美媒指廣電總局無解釋原因<br />\n中共封殺維尼　新片禁映<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180805/large/a0401a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180805%2Flarge%2Fa0401a.gif&h=332da6d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n【本報訊】全球最新上映的迪士尼經典動畫《小熊維尼》真人版電影《維尼與我》（Christopher Robin），疑因中國國家主席習近平屢被嘲笑體態激似小熊維尼，美媒爆料指該齣合家歡電影已遭中共封殺，中國版譯名就算譯為《克里斯托弗．羅賓》避提小熊維尼，電影依然無法進軍內地。深圳有戲院職員向《蘋果》記者透露，暫時沒收到播映通知，內地網民擔憂電影上映無期。<br />\n<br />\n記者：廖智廣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n習近平與小熊維尼的「恩怨」起始於2013年，習當年訪美與時任美國總統奧巴馬的一張合照，因其體態與步調酷似小熊維尼，旋即被網民拼圖取笑，維尼因「冒犯」領導人遂成內地敏感詞，當局去年更在社交媒體封鎖小熊維尼的圖片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180805/large/05la4p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180805%2Flarge%2F05la4p3.jpg&h=cf8b5a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■日前已在港上映的《維尼與我》無法進軍內地。何頴賢攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180805/large/a0401b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180805%2Flarge%2Fa0401b.gif&h=bda2a136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《再見小熊心》只能在愛奇藝等影片網播放。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳媒避忌稱「xiao熊Winnie」<br />\n<br />\n捲入這次封殺風波的《維尼與我》，故事講述主人翁羅賓長大成人後與維尼再次相遇的故事，在本港被評為一級片，代表適合所有年齡人士觀看。據稱，內地原本擬定8月初與台灣、香港、美國同步上映，還展開連串宣傳，電影譯名及簡介煞費苦心避提小熊維尼，改稱《克里斯托弗．羅賓》，豆瓣電影介紹對小熊維尼等敏感字眼隻字不提。<br />\n<br />\n專門報道荷李活娛樂圈消息的美國媒體Hollywood Reporter前日報道，指《維尼與我》不獲批准在中國上映，國家廣播電視總局沒有解釋原因，報道引述消息指，禁止上映電影與去年中共封殺小熊維尼有關，也成為今年唯一一齣不獲中國放行的迪士尼電影。報道又引述內部人士提出另類解釋，指受中國對海外電影上映配額限制，該片才未能獲批上映。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180805/large/a0401c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180805%2Flarge%2Fa0401c.gif&h=7108a1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年3月，內地電影雜誌《環球銀幕》在官方微博表示內地計劃引進該電影，微博在劇情介紹僅以拼音提及小熊維尼，包括「該片以xiao熊Winnie為題材」、「有隻小熊的好朋友羅賓從小男孩長大成人」，可惜的是，就算避忌正面提及小熊維尼，「計劃引進」的結果依然是上映無期。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者昨進入內地電影網追查，正在上映及即將上映的欄目均未見《維尼與我》，記者昨致電深圳多家戲院查詢，有職員透露沒收到《維尼與我》播映通知，另有戲院職員稱該片暫時沒上映計劃，一旦接到消息應會上映。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《再見小熊心》亦不能上映<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，另一部於去年10月在英國上映、本港今年3月上映，講述英國作家創作小熊維尼過程的電影《再見小熊心》（Goodbye Christopher Robin，內地譯名《再見，克里斯托弗．羅賓》），同樣令內地戲迷失望未有上映，只有愛奇藝等影片網站提供網上播放。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n影視股急瀉　蒸發數百億<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n港列一級片　上映3日收211萬"},{"pid":"8c068545fcd648e5d87a6e13cd63db522aac0211","tid":767843,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffd30b485d40519bf31625dee2d3448ae575704","tid":767843,"uid":51701,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:52:07.000Z","msg":"愈搞愈多人知雜總<br />\n<br />\n支那人由上到下都係玻璃心"},{"pid":"38db9839099241e2dfb595f449946a9e1b27253c","tid":767843,"uid":29041,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:53:49.000Z","msg":"日日都話人地貿易保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,但自己記"},{"pid":"d8c691b2590f59b8db50235a19c23f79e2e506f0","tid":767843,"uid":23635,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:54:26.000Z","msg":"強国，只容許有一隻維尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6797e7093a2b47930ea310e93b0b3c4bf2ce52e0","tid":767843,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:57:10.000Z","msg":"不用去別國干涉內政"},{"pid":"d73996da59c3a8fd84a38939f1e2a7a8a33bef15","tid":767843,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6797e7093a2b47930ea310e93b0b3c4bf2ce52e0","tid":767843,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:57:10.000Z","msg":"不用去別國干涉內政"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:57:36.000Z","msg":"不容許別國干涉內政"},{"pid":"3cf7130eea660fb8a9b775988845cdd1b41b0500","tid":767843,"uid":51701,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T02:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/BwqgoMVIAAAOES6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FBwqgoMVIAAAOES6.jpg&h=b50135e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af3e88600bfaaee6af8ab0dbcd683278b3f73cad","tid":767843,"uid":30169,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T02:34:06.000Z","msg":"自由貿易？屌你老母啦支那！"},{"pid":"a30423423d439cc36741f9e14e9522e8700b34ce","tid":767843,"uid":1556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T02:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\